{"video_id": "04EA3ny2Bns", "title": "OVERCOME SOCIAL MEDIA ADDICTION | HG Amitasana Das | GITA LIFE Live | HKM Mumbai", "speaker": "HG Amitasana Dasa", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=04EA3ny2Bns", "duration": 607, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 29.98, "text": " Thank you."}, {"start": 30.0, "end": 42.36, "text": " For today's Gita Live session, the topic for the day is Overcoming Social Media Addiction."}, {"start": 44.58, "end": 49.86, "text": " Social media has become a very, very integral part of our lives."}, {"start": 50.72, "end": 56.519999999999996, "text": " Even if we want to, it is difficult to live without it."}, {"start": 57.36, "end": 59.28, "text": " We all know there are"}, {"start": 59.28, "end": 59.980000000000004, "text": " many"}, {"start": 59.980000000000004, "end": 61.7, "text": " many benefits"}, {"start": 61.7, "end": 64.52000000000001, "text": " and we also know"}, {"start": 64.52000000000001, "end": 67.28, "text": " that it has many, many"}, {"start": 67.28, "end": 69.74000000000001, "text": " bad effects."}, {"start": 70.56, "end": 73.0, "text": " It can even lead to addictions."}, {"start": 74.18, "end": 77.02000000000001, "text": " So today we are going to talk more about this subject"}, {"start": 77.02000000000001, "end": 79.52000000000001, "text": " and we will also share"}, {"start": 79.52000000000001, "end": 82.10000000000001, "text": " perspectives from the Gita"}, {"start": 82.10000000000001, "end": 83.02000000000001, "text": " why"}, {"start": 83.02000000000001, "end": 86.06, "text": " people are getting addicted to it."}, {"start": 86.52000000000001, "end": 87.80000000000001, "text": " What is the root cause?"}, {"start": 87.8, "end": 96.0, "text": " And from the Gita, we will also get some clue as to how we can handle these tools"}, {"start": 96.0, "end": 102.0, "text": " intelligently, effectively, without these tools harming us."}, {"start": 102.0, "end": 106.0, "text": " So before we get into the discussion, let us all pray together."}, {"start": 106.0, "end": 108.0, "text": " Please join me in offering the prayers."}, {"start": 108.0, "end": 117.0, "text": " Let us all fold our hands together and please repeat the prayers after me as we display the prayers on the screen."}, {"start": 117.8, "end": 126.0, "text": " Namah Om Vishnupadaya Krishna Prishtaya Bhutale"}, {"start": 126.0, "end": 133.0, "text": " Srimate Bhaktivedanta Swaminiti Namine"}, {"start": 133.0, "end": 140.0, "text": " Namaste Saraswate Deve Gauravani Pracharine"}, {"start": 140.0, "end": 147.0, "text": " Nirvishesha Shunyavadi Pashchati Deshatarine"}, {"start": 147.0, "end": 152.0, "text": " Jai Shri Krishna Chaitanya"}, {"start": 152.0, "end": 155.0, "text": " Prabhu Nithyananda"}, {"start": 155.0, "end": 158.0, "text": " Shri Advaita Gadadhara"}, {"start": 158.0, "end": 163.0, "text": " Sri Vasadi Gaurabhakta Vrinda"}, {"start": 163.0, "end": 166.0, "text": " Namo Mahavadanyaya"}, {"start": 166.0, "end": 170.0, "text": " Krishna Prema Pradayate"}, {"start": 170.0, "end": 172.0, "text": " Please repeat after me."}, {"start": 172.0, "end": 176.0, "text": " Krishna Ya Krishna Chaitanya"}, {"start": 176.0, "end": 180.0, "text": " Namne Gauratushe Namaha"}, {"start": 180.0, "end": 184.0, "text": " Namo Brahmane Devaya"}, {"start": 184.0, "end": 188.0, "text": " Go Brahmane Hitayacha"}, {"start": 188.0, "end": 192.0, "text": " Jagadhitaya Krishnaya"}, {"start": 192.0, "end": 196.0, "text": " Govindaya Namo Namaha"}, {"start": 196.0, "end": 200.0, "text": " He Krishna Karuna Sindho"}, {"start": 200.0, "end": 203.0, "text": " Dina Bandhu Jagatpate"}, {"start": 203.0, "end": 207.0, "text": " Gopesha Gopika Kanta"}, {"start": 207.0, "end": 211.0, "text": " Radha Kanta Namostute"}, {"start": 211.0, "end": 215.0, "text": " Tapta Kanchan Gaurangi"}, {"start": 215.0, "end": 218.0, "text": " Radhe Vrindavaneshwari"}, {"start": 218.0, "end": 222.0, "text": " Vrishabhanu Sute Devi"}, {"start": 222.0, "end": 225.0, "text": " Pranamami Hari Priye"}, {"start": 225.0, "end": 230.0, "text": " Vancha Kalpata Rubhyascha"}, {"start": 230.0, "end": 233.0, "text": " Kripa Sindhu Bhyaivacha"}, {"start": 233.0, "end": 237.0, "text": " Patita Naam Pavnebhyo"}, {"start": 237.0, "end": 241.0, "text": " Vaishnavebhyo Namo Namaha"}, {"start": 241.0, "end": 245.0, "text": " Hare Krishna Hare Krishna"}, {"start": 245.0, "end": 248.0, "text": " Krishna Krishna Hare Hare"}, {"start": 248.0, "end": 251.0, "text": " Hare Rama Hare Rama"}, {"start": 251.0, "end": 255.0, "text": " Rama Rama Hare Hare"}, {"start": 259.0, "end": 262.0, "text": " This is a very interesting and relevant topic"}, {"start": 262.0, "end": 265.0, "text": " more so in present times."}, {"start": 265.0, "end": 268.0, "text": " We all know"}, {"start": 268.0, "end": 271.0, "text": " people in general"}, {"start": 271.0, "end": 274.0, "text": " spend inordinate amount of time"}, {"start": 274.0, "end": 277.0, "text": " in front of their smartphones"}, {"start": 277.0, "end": 280.0, "text": " and these days there are many apps"}, {"start": 280.0, "end": 283.0, "text": " many social media platforms"}, {"start": 283.0, "end": 286.0, "text": " which if we get into"}, {"start": 286.0, "end": 289.0, "text": " eat up lot of our time."}, {"start": 289.0, "end": 292.0, "text": " Now is it really bad"}, {"start": 292.0, "end": 295.0, "text": " to be on the social media"}, {"start": 295.0, "end": 297.0, "text": " to be on Facebook"}, {"start": 297.0, "end": 299.0, "text": " to be on Instagram"}, {"start": 299.0, "end": 301.0, "text": " is it wrong?"}, {"start": 301.0, "end": 303.0, "text": " The answer is no."}, {"start": 303.0, "end": 305.0, "text": " It's not wrong."}, {"start": 305.0, "end": 307.0, "text": " It's something like asking"}, {"start": 307.0, "end": 309.0, "text": " is a knife bad?"}, {"start": 311.0, "end": 313.0, "text": " Depends on who is using"}, {"start": 313.0, "end": 315.0, "text": " and how he is using it."}, {"start": 315.0, "end": 317.0, "text": " If the knife is"}, {"start": 317.0, "end": 319.0, "text": " in the hand of a surgeon"}, {"start": 319.0, "end": 321.0, "text": " the same knife can save a life."}, {"start": 322.0, "end": 324.0, "text": " But the same knife"}, {"start": 324.0, "end": 326.0, "text": " in wrong hands"}, {"start": 326.0, "end": 328.0, "text": " can even take someone's life"}, {"start": 328.0, "end": 330.0, "text": " can kill someone."}, {"start": 330.0, "end": 333.0, "text": " So knife per se is not good or bad"}, {"start": 333.0, "end": 336.0, "text": " a lot depends on how we use it"}, {"start": 336.0, "end": 339.0, "text": " how intelligently or unintelligently"}, {"start": 339.0, "end": 341.0, "text": " we use that knife."}, {"start": 341.0, "end": 345.0, "text": " Same is true with all social media platforms."}, {"start": 345.0, "end": 348.0, "text": " They have lot of benefits."}, {"start": 348.0, "end": 351.0, "text": " There is lot of advantages"}, {"start": 351.0, "end": 354.0, "text": " which we can"}, {"start": 354.0, "end": 357.0, "text": " get out of these social media platforms."}, {"start": 357.0, "end": 358.0, "text": " I'll just share few of them"}, {"start": 358.0, "end": 360.0, "text": " before we talk about addiction"}, {"start": 360.0, "end": 361.0, "text": " and things like that"}, {"start": 361.0, "end": 363.0, "text": " something on the negative side."}, {"start": 363.0, "end": 365.0, "text": " Let us be judicious"}, {"start": 365.0, "end": 366.0, "text": " and also count on"}, {"start": 366.0, "end": 367.0, "text": " some of the good things"}, {"start": 367.0, "end": 372.0, "text": " which these platforms have done."}, {"start": 372.0, "end": 376.0, "text": " This reminds me of my college days."}, {"start": 376.0, "end": 380.0, "text": " This was in the year 1988-89"}, {"start": 380.0, "end": 383.0, "text": " when I was doing my engineering."}, {"start": 383.0, "end": 386.0, "text": " Those days the mode of communication"}, {"start": 386.0, "end": 388.0, "text": " was letters."}, {"start": 388.0, "end": 390.0, "text": " I still remember there was"}, {"start": 390.0, "end": 391.0, "text": " a postcard"}, {"start": 391.0, "end": 393.0, "text": " 15 paise postcard"}, {"start": 393.0, "end": 395.0, "text": " and you would scribble something"}, {"start": 395.0, "end": 398.0, "text": " and put it in a post box."}, {"start": 398.0, "end": 400.0, "text": " There was a post box"}, {"start": 400.0, "end": 402.0, "text": " right next to our hostel"}, {"start": 402.0, "end": 405.0, "text": " and you post it in"}, {"start": 405.0, "end": 407.0, "text": " and then after 5 days"}, {"start": 407.0, "end": 408.0, "text": " 6 days or 7 days"}, {"start": 408.0, "end": 410.0, "text": " the postcard will reach"}, {"start": 410.0, "end": 412.0, "text": " the destination."}, {"start": 412.0, "end": 414.0, "text": " I used to write to my parents"}, {"start": 414.0, "end": 417.0, "text": " and near India ones."}, {"start": 417.0, "end": 418.0, "text": " It would reach after 4-5 days."}, {"start": 418.0, "end": 420.0, "text": " So if you have to communicate something"}, {"start": 420.0, "end": 422.0, "text": " the message will reach the other side"}, {"start": 422.0, "end": 425.0, "text": " after 5 or 6 days."}, {"start": 425.0, "end": 427.0, "text": " If you have travelled from your home town"}, {"start": 427.0, "end": 428.0, "text": " to the college"}, {"start": 428.0, "end": 429.0, "text": " they have no clue"}, {"start": 429.0, "end": 432.0, "text": " whether you have reached safely."}, {"start": 432.0, "end": 434.0, "text": " And invariably we used to write"}, {"start": 434.0, "end": 436.0, "text": " some kind of letters or postcard"}, {"start": 436.0, "end": 437.0, "text": " and it will take 4-5 days."}, {"start": 437.0, "end": 439.0, "text": " Till that time you can"}, {"start": 439.0, "end": 441.0, "text": " assume that yes the person"}, {"start": 441.0, "end": 442.0, "text": " has reached safely"}, {"start": 442.0, "end": 444.0, "text": " or the person is fine."}, {"start": 444.0, "end": 446.0, "text": " I remember in those days"}, {"start": 446.0, "end": 448.0, "text": " we used to"}, {"start": 448.0, "end": 450.0, "text": " for some urgent matters"}, {"start": 450.0, "end": 451.0, "text": " or some urgent news"}, {"start": 451.0, "end": 452.0, "text": " suppose some"}, {"start": 452.0, "end": 454.0, "text": " let's say there is a death in the family"}, {"start": 454.0, "end": 455.0, "text": " it has to be communicated"}, {"start": 455.0, "end": 457.0, "text": " there was something called as telegram."}, {"start": 457.0, "end": 460.0, "text": " These days you also have a telegram app"}, {"start": 460.0, "end": 462.0, "text": " but those days the telegram was"}, {"start": 462.0, "end": 464.0, "text": " you have to go to a post office"}, {"start": 464.0, "end": 466.0, "text": " and you have to write"}, {"start": 466.0, "end": 467.0, "text": " what message you want to send."}, {"start": 467.0, "end": 468.0, "text": " Each word"}, {"start": 468.0, "end": 470.0, "text": " for each letter counts."}, {"start": 470.0, "end": 473.0, "text": " There is some paisa associated"}, {"start": 473.0, "end": 474.0, "text": " with each letter"}, {"start": 474.0, "end": 476.0, "text": " so you have to be very judicious"}, {"start": 476.0, "end": 478.0, "text": " because the longer the sentence"}, {"start": 478.0, "end": 480.0, "text": " the longer the number of words"}, {"start": 480.0, "end": 482.0, "text": " more is the money involved."}, {"start": 482.0, "end": 484.0, "text": " So you are very judicious"}, {"start": 484.0, "end": 486.0, "text": " you will eat the words"}, {"start": 486.0, "end": 489.0, "text": " and you will draft the message"}, {"start": 489.0, "end": 491.0, "text": " and for each word"}, {"start": 491.0, "end": 493.0, "text": " for a small telegram"}, {"start": 493.0, "end": 494.0, "text": " with 2 or 3 sentences"}, {"start": 494.0, "end": 495.0, "text": " or 4 sentences"}, {"start": 495.0, "end": 497.0, "text": " in those days"}, {"start": 497.0, "end": 498.0, "text": " it would cost some"}, {"start": 498.0, "end": 499.0, "text": " 30 rupees"}, {"start": 499.0, "end": 500.0, "text": " 40 rupees"}, {"start": 500.0, "end": 501.0, "text": " or 50 rupees."}, {"start": 501.0, "end": 504.0, "text": " And you will go to the post office"}, {"start": 504.0, "end": 506.0, "text": " write the whole thing"}, {"start": 506.0, "end": 508.0, "text": " and then there will be a person"}, {"start": 508.0, "end": 509.0, "text": " who will type it out"}, {"start": 509.0, "end": 513.0, "text": " and through that mechanism of telegraph"}, {"start": 513.0, "end": 514.0, "text": " the technology"}, {"start": 514.0, "end": 515.0, "text": " whatever it was"}, {"start": 515.0, "end": 517.0, "text": " the same message would be typed"}, {"start": 517.0, "end": 520.0, "text": " on the telegraph machine"}, {"start": 520.0, "end": 522.0, "text": " at the recipient town"}, {"start": 522.0, "end": 524.0, "text": " or the city"}, {"start": 524.0, "end": 527.0, "text": " and the postman would go and deliver it"}, {"start": 527.0, "end": 528.0, "text": " over the telegraph"}, {"start": 528.0, "end": 530.0, "text": " on an urgent basis"}, {"start": 530.0, "end": 534.0, "text": " to the person whom you want to communicate to."}, {"start": 534.0, "end": 536.0, "text": " So in best case scenario"}, {"start": 536.0, "end": 538.0, "text": " you are able to transmit the message"}, {"start": 538.0, "end": 540.0, "text": " that to one or two sentences"}, {"start": 540.0, "end": 542.0, "text": " same day to the person"}, {"start": 542.0, "end": 544.0, "text": " but at a very very"}, {"start": 544.0, "end": 546.0, "text": " additional high cost."}, {"start": 546.0, "end": 548.0, "text": " And then"}, {"start": 548.0, "end": 550.0, "text": " a revolution came"}, {"start": 550.0, "end": 552.0, "text": " this was in the year 1990"}, {"start": 552.0, "end": 554.0, "text": " somewhere around that time"}, {"start": 554.0, "end": 556.0, "text": " STD ISD started"}, {"start": 556.0, "end": 558.0, "text": " becoming very popular."}, {"start": 558.0, "end": 560.0, "text": " First time we could speak"}, {"start": 560.0, "end": 561.0, "text": " to our near and dear ones"}, {"start": 561.0, "end": 562.0, "text": " go to an STD booth"}, {"start": 562.0, "end": 563.0, "text": " and those days"}, {"start": 563.0, "end": 565.0, "text": " since the technology was new"}, {"start": 565.0, "end": 567.0, "text": " for every second"}, {"start": 567.0, "end": 569.0, "text": " there was a pulse"}, {"start": 569.0, "end": 570.0, "text": " 2 second pulse"}, {"start": 570.0, "end": 571.0, "text": " 4 second pulse"}, {"start": 571.0, "end": 572.0, "text": " and for each pulse"}, {"start": 572.0, "end": 575.0, "text": " there was certain amount fixed"}, {"start": 575.0, "end": 577.0, "text": " and there was time zones"}, {"start": 577.0, "end": 579.0, "text": " in the morning before 6 am"}, {"start": 579.0, "end": 581.0, "text": " it was 4 second pulse"}, {"start": 581.0, "end": 583.0, "text": " after 6 to 10 am"}, {"start": 583.0, "end": 585.0, "text": " it was 2 second pulse"}, {"start": 585.0, "end": 586.0, "text": " and after day time"}, {"start": 586.0, "end": 588.0, "text": " regular business hours"}, {"start": 588.0, "end": 589.0, "text": " it was 1 second pulse"}, {"start": 589.0, "end": 591.0, "text": " depending on the distance."}, {"start": 591.0, "end": 593.0, "text": " I remember even if you speak for 2 minutes"}, {"start": 593.0, "end": 594.0, "text": " or 1 minute"}, {"start": 594.0, "end": 597.0, "text": " the bill would be as high as 50 rupees"}, {"start": 597.0, "end": 599.0, "text": " 100 rupees."}, {"start": 599.0, "end": 601.0, "text": " In those days when"}, {"start": 601.0, "end": 603.0, "text": " full semester"}, {"start": 603.0, "end": 605.0, "text": " we used to spend about 4000-5000 rupees"}, {"start": 605.0, "end": 607.0, "text": " per month around 1000 rupees."}]}